  <div class="ds-tab 4658 original_html selected" >
    <div class="ds-tab-note" >Example notes or example HTML without markup.</div>
    <pre class="ds-tab-content prettyprint lang-html linenums clipsource ">
&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;Laptop Battery Replacement&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;A consumable battery for Model X&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;GTIN: 5901234123457&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Category: Consumable&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;Virtual Pump Twin&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Digital Twin of the physical water pump for simulation&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;DID: did:web:example.com:product:pump-twin-001&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Category: Digital Twin&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;
  &lt;h2&gt;CRM Module&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Software module for customer relationship management&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;DID: did:web:example.com:product:crm-module-001&lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Category: Software Component&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
  </div>
  
  
  <div class="ds-tab 4658 microdata " itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/SoftwareSourceCode">
    <link itemprop="codeRepository" href="https://github.com/schemaorg/schemaorg/" />
    <meta itemprop="codeSampleType" content="snippet" />
