&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div vocab=&#34;https://schema.org/&#34; typeof=&#34;SoftwareApplication&#34;&gt;
  &lt;h2 property=&#34;name&#34;&gt;CRM Module&lt;/h2&gt;
  &lt;p property=&#34;description&#34;&gt;Software module for customer relationship management&lt;/p&gt;
