  <div class="ds-tab eg-4505 original_html selected" >
    <div class="ds-tab-note" >Example notes or example HTML without markup.</div>
    <pre class="ds-tab-content prettyprint lang-html linenums clipsource ">
&lt;strong&gt;Château Snotty 2020&lt;/strong&gt;

The snottiest red wine on the market.
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Organic red wine, made in France&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2020 Vintage, a very interesting year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;75 cl bottle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cru du Pichet d&#39;Or&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Best before 2026&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contains Sulfite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Please recycle the glass bottle&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</pre>
  </div>
  
  
  
  
  <div class="ds-tab eg-4505 jsonld " itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/SoftwareSourceCode">
